All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Administrator
Represents an Administrator in the hospital system, managing hospital staff, appointments, and inventory.
App
The App class represents the main entry point of the hospital management system.
Appointment
Represents an appointment made between a doctor and a patient.
AppointmentManagementInterface
The AppointmentManagementInterface provides the contract for managing and viewing appointment details.
AppointmentOutcome
The AppointmentOutcome class represents the outcome of a patient's appointment.
BloodType
The BloodType enum represents the different human blood types based on the ABO and RhD classification systems that our patients in the hospital can have.
Doctor
Represents a Doctor in a hospital.
Gender
The Gender enum represents the two primary genders used for classification in the system: Male and Female.
Hospital
The Hospital class manages the operations and entities in a hospital system.
HospitalStaff
The HospitalStaff class represents a staff member of a hospital.
ImportMed
The ImportMed class provides methods to read the medicine stock from CSV files.
ImportUsers
The ImportUsers class provides methods to read patients and from CSV files.
InventoryManagementInterface
Interface to define the methods for managing the inventory of medicines.
MedicalHistory
The MedicalHistory class holds information about a patient's past medical history.
MedicalRecord
The MedicalRecord class represents the medical record of a patient.
MedicineStock
The MedicineStock class represents a medicine item in a pharmacy or hospital stock system.
Menu
The Menu class provides methods to print various menus for different user roles in the Hospital Management System.
Password
A class to manage password updates, password hashing, and storage of passwords in a CSV file.
Patient
Represents a Patient in the hospital system.
Pharmacist
The Pharmacist class represents a pharmacist in the hospital system.
PrescribedMedication
The PrescribedMedication class represents a prescribed medication for a patient.
ReplenishmentRequest
Represents a request for replenishing a medicine stock in the hospital's inventory.
Role
Class representing a role within the system.
StaffManagementInterface
Interface for managing hospital staff within the system.
StatusOfAppointment
The StatusOfAppointment enum represents the possible statuses of an appointment in the hospital.
StatusOfPrescribedMedication
The StatusOfPrescribedMedication enum represents the possible statuses of a prescribed medication of a patient.
TimeSlot
The TimeSlot class represents a time interval within a specific date, defined by a start time and an end time.
